Create the recordId

To store the ID of the work item in the flow, create the recordId variable.

For Resource Type, select Variable.
For API Name, enter recordId. Note: Make sure to use this name, specifically.
For Data Type, select Text.
Under Availability Outside the Flow, select Available for input.
Click Done.
